SimplyPHP
1. MVC Structure
   . system	Framework Root
     + core Core module folder
     + app	Application folder
       + model 		appname.class.php
         + handler
           + appname/methodname.inc.php
           + methodname.inc.php
       + views
         + appname/methodname.tpl.php
         + methodname.tpl.php
       + controller
       + conf   application configure folder
         + database.php

   
2. URL Parse
   . URL Format	http://domain.com/path1/path2/...?query_string
   . Mapping	controller->mapping(), this function can be orverride by user's controller
     . domain	=> Application model
     . path1	=> method
     . path2..	=> parameter stack
   . View	controlled by app variable this->stream['view']
     . Default	views/class/method.tpl.php
     . Share	views/method.tpl.php
     . Customize	via overridding this->stream
   . Output
     . Binding		view,data,format(html,ajax,...);
     . Application	$this->stream = array('view'=>view_name,'data'=>app_data,'format'=>format);

I. Reserved Word
   . Generally, names with prefix '_sp_' are reserved for SimplyPHP, e.g. $_sp_STACK,...
   . _ENTRY  Controller URL convertion

